contentfulCollection.seoDescription: Organic heavyweight cotton, sweater & sherpa fleece. All available at radically low prices. Because you deserve it.
contentfulCollection.name: The Fleece Collection

content.value: Our heavyweight hoodie. To ensure max durability and an ultra-soft feel, we created our own custom 375g woven fleece from 100% organic cotton. Merging form and function, we built the front pocket internally with a hidden cell-phone pocket for a clean, modern look.
Made from recycled water bottles, these jackets have it all - comfy, sustainable & affordable.
